Title: No Doubt
Plot: Jenna feels like she and Matty are actually on solid ground for the first time when he asks her out on their first real date. But, when Tamara reveals her suspicion that Matty wrote Jenna's care-frontation letter, Jenna starts to question everything about her romance with Matty.
ParentalRatingReason: M Sex scenes and offensive language
Writer: Kelly Fullerton, Cassie Pappas, Meredith Philpott
GuestStars: Jessica Lu, Greer Grammer, Michael Bachmann, Natalia Castellanos
